{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "10", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "14", "M": "40", "S": "47"}}, "news": [{"title": "Nagpur civic body plans offer up to 15% rebate as 44% property owners avail tax sops", "para": "The Nagpur Municipal Corporation (NMC) plans to reintroduce property tax rebates of up to 15% following last year's success, where nearly 44% of property holders availed the incentive. The proposed structure aims to maximize early collections and promote digital payments, offering 15% and 10% rebates for payments by June 30, 2026.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/nagpur-municipal-corporation-offers-up-to-15-property-tax-rebate-to-boost-compliance/130166423?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-65720/130166423.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Lucknow development body to offer over 2,000 plots in first phase of new housing scheme", "para": "The Lucknow Development Authority (LDA) is set to launch the Varun Vihar housing scheme in June, offering approximately 2,100 plots in its initial phase. Developed over 2,270 hectares along the Agra expressway, the scheme's land acquisition is progressing through mutual consent. Online registrations will commence post-launch.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/lucknow-development-body-to-offer-over-2000-plots-in-first-phase-of-new-housing-scheme/130166350?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-224838/130166350.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Mysuru development body earns \u20b9156 crore as buyers lap up premium sites", "para": "Mysuru Development Authority (MDA) generated Rs 156 crore from auctioning 133 out of 200 commercial and residential sites. Buyers showed strong interest across Mysuru, particularly in West Mysuru where sites fetched Rs 13,000 per sqft. Vasanth Nagar also saw significant interest, with 33 of 40 sites sold.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/mysuru-development-authority-achieves-156-crore-from-premium-site-auctions/130166258?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-26838/130166258.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}